<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79f581aa-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s4728"><num value="4728">§ 4728.</num><heading> Brown tree snake control program</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Task Force shall, within the program developed under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s4722/a">section 4722(a) of this title</ref>, undertake a comprehensive, environmentally sound program in coordination with regional, territorial, State and local entities to control the brown tree snake (Boiga irregularis) in Guam and other areas where the species is established outside of its historic range.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79f581ab-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/646/tI/s1209">Pub. L. 101–646, title I, § 1209</ref>, <date date="1990-11-29">Nov. 29, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/4772">104 Stat. 4772</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/104/332/s2/h/1">Pub. L. 104–332, § 2(h)(1)</ref>, <date date="1996-10-26">Oct. 26, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/4091">110 Stat. 4091</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/263/dK/tCXIII/s11327/e/5">Pub. L. 117–263, div. K, title CXIII, § 11327(e)(5)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-23">Dec. 23, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/4098">136 Stat. 4098</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id79f581ac-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
